{"tid":1871662,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"愛·國家之肺炎速遞","createTime":"2020-02-09T15:09:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T00:45:09.000Z","uid":285843,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7d068cc9527fd3d342b9aa4e0e194246652f429e","tid":1871662,"uid":285843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T15:09:13.000Z","msg":"代po 我契爺好有才華 老而不廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />頭先有感而發，真係忍唔住，要寫出我既心聲：<br />\n<br />\n人人防疫似發癲<br />\n撲罩滿天<br />\n酒精廁紙搶哂<br />\n如同大戰！<br />\n唔用罩就咪話再見<br />\n像坐監困足每一天<br />\n成頭霉<br />\n係絕境的標誌!<br />\n<br />\n鬧爆政府<br />\n個腦載屎<br />\n偏私、固執、黐線<br />\n如同弱智！<br />\n林鄭冇道理係要撐<br />\n為了「面」決不去封關<br />\n全城攬炒冇當我地係人<br />\n高官好快著草<br />\n紫荊花玩到謝就殘<br />\n想迫個個去燒炭！"},{"pid":"adc4cf6ee982969c4111c3a24d7e61bdacd7357d","tid":1871662,"uid":190957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T16:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解可以咁唔啱音"},{"pid":"23d747223c4cf71f2a708c7e3a99c548ded8de3f","tid":1871662,"uid":285843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adc4cf6ee982969c4111c3a24d7e61bdacd7357d","tid":1871662,"uid":190957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T16:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解可以咁唔啱音"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T00:45:09.000Z","msg":"契爺年代既曲風係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}